  "title": "Critical realism and systematic dialectics: a reply to Andrew Brown",
  "abstract": "In ‘Approach with caution: critical realism in social research’, Andrew Brown sets out a series of criticisms of critical realism from the perspective of systematic dialectics. This current article is one critical realist’s reply to Brown.",
